{
  "stem": "1062.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Once-- it was in also 1944, in January in 1944-- I get up in the morning, I go to work and I see in the city of Satu Mare the German Army was there.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Hungary was occupied in March 1944, but it was an occupation where that's all you saw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Trucks, tanks, cars, bicycles, motorcycles, all military, parked on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Without any rhyme or reason, all over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Everybody was staying indoor, but I went to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so I went into my shop, and I remember a German officer coming in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he asked something, but my Hungarian boss didn't understand them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But since I spoke Yiddish, I could understand a little German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I asked him what he wants.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he said it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His, his car-- he had a problem with the car.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Something broke down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we went out and we fixed it, and he was very much impressed with me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then he said to me, where there is a restaurant in town?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I told them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the problem was that right away, they gave out a law that all the Jews had to wear a yellow star.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if you didn't have the yellow star on, you couldn't-- you couldn't go any place because you were subject to arrest and worse.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So everybody had a star.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So while I worked in my-- in the shop, I didn't have my jacket on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I couldn't go out without my jacket, I'd be without the star.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I put on my jacket, and the German officer sees that I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Didn't bother him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only thing is, he didn't let be sit in-- because I took him to the restaurant, he didn't let me sit in-- inside the car.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he put me on the fender.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was sitting on the fender and I was pointing the driver where to go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a place called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a little restaurant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went in. and the two-- and the two-- and the two officers-- and the two officers went ahead, and, and they sat down for, for, for, for, whatever they ate.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told me at a table I should sit at that table.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hungarian police pass by, and the Hungarian police sees a Jewish man, a Jewish boy, with a star, sitting in the restaurant.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They got very excited.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They rush into the restaurant and they're ready to kill me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The German officer gets up and he says-- because the Hungarian police, they had feathers on their-- they had black hats and feathers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the German officer tells the Hungarian police, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That means, what does the rooster want, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he threw him out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he was-- you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then a law came out that no Jew is allowed to go out on the street, everybody had to go back home.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we heard rumors that in some places, they were starting to round up the Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I walked back to my village because you couldn't take a bus anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I walk back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when I came back to my village, it was Passover.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Passover, 1944.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we were home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We heard rumors the German soldiers are beating Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They're arresting Jews, and all kinds of rumors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at night, we wouldn't sleep in our homes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We would go and sleep by the, by the Christians, by the Romanian people at night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was the last-- Passover was the-- Passover, I remember, was like, on a Saturday.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Sunday morning, in my village there is-- you know, there is what we call a village crier.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The village crier has a, has a drum.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He carries a drum, and he beats the drum.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When he beats the drum, people hear the drum, everybody comes out to hear what he has to say, because there were no newspapers and no radio.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he beats the drum.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we all go out to hear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the village crier says that all Jewish people, all men over 16 years old, should go to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then about 15 minutes later, he comes back and he says, all women and men over 16 should come back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then about a half an hour later, because he didn't have the-- he had the orders himself, like.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the Jewish people-- men, women and children-- to go to the synagogue immediately.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I want you to know something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's another question here where, where, where-- you know, they say to you, listen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Next week, you go there and there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Right away, you go to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The impact, we knew something is happening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nobody ever imagined what's going to come.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
